videos.description: Naji Marshall attacks the rim and hits a tough reverse layup for Xavier's first basket.
videos.headline: Marshall gets fancy for Xavier bucket

videos.description: Jamorko Pickett knocks down a 3-pointer from the left corner to give Georgetown a two-point lead at the half.
videos.headline: Pickett drills 3-pointer before buzzer

videos.description: Jamorko Pickett knocks down a step-back 3-pointer, his fifth of the game.
videos.headline: Pickett drains step-back 3-pointer

videos.description: Jamorko Pickett gets into the passing lane for a steal before Trey Dickerson's attacks the rim for and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: Steal leads to Dickerson and-1 bucket

videos.description: Naji Marshall drills a 3-pointer with a defender in his face to open a 14-point lead against Georgetown late in the second half.
videos.headline: Marshall 3 gives Xavier 14-point lead
